title: Marijuana Causes Brain Damage: Scientific Facts.
description:
[This is a high-resolution version of a video that was first "rushed-to-upload" under another title, and at lower quality.]

A stack of peer-reviewed sources presented in response to "Mic. the Vegan", who made a video titled: "Is Marijuana Unhealthy? An In-Depth Look at the Research".
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DOzvgmBapZ8

The link to the article that started it all (from my old blog, vegan-mind-tricks) is here:
vegan-mind-tricks.tumblr.com/post/58138831334/brain-damage-caused-by-cannabis-adult-and-infant
You can find all of the peer-reviewed sources either by clicking through the links in that article, just linked-to above, or by looking up the sources via the info shown on-screen in the video itself (really, you can see the  "D.O.I." number, along with the title, authors' names, publication, etc., on-screen for each one).
